{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240020/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1738253137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240020/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1738253137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mansion Mayhem is a zombie survival FPS set in a vast mansion. Battle hordes of undead with an array of weapons in intense, endless shooting action. Fight through your limits and defeat massive hordes with powerful guns!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240020/extras/BT_Text_Steam_BLAST_EN.png?t=1738253137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240020/extras/mansione.gif?t=1738253137\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Mansion Mayhem</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mansion Mayhem is a heart-pounding zombie survival FPS set within the eerie confines of a sprawling mansion. As the undead swarm the dark hallways and rooms, you\u2019ll need to use a diverse arsenal of weapons to fend off relentless hordes. Explore the mansion\u2019s labyrinthine layout, uncovering new challenges and secrets with every corner you turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240020/extras/BT_Text_Steam_MAIM_EN.png?t=1738253137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240020/extras/9af96107bb838d6db1eb11f6ac34bda9-ezgif.com-overlay.gif?t=1738253137\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragra